---
title: Dynamic cluster membership (ADR-0066)
---
flowchart TB
  COORD["Coordinator"]
  MAP["Versioned shard map<br/>(epoch N)"]
  ADD["Add / remove shard"]
  NEWMAP["Shard map epoch N+1"]
  ROUTER["Router"]
  REBAL["Online rebalance<br/>(migration handshake)"]
  COORD --> MAP
  ADD --> COORD --> NEWMAP
  NEWMAP -->|propagate| ROUTER
  NEWMAP --> REBAL
  ROUTER -. refresh on epoch change .-> NEWMAP
